2) Infrastructure (Linux/unix based editing, monitiroring and command based tools)
3) Cloud- Infrasturcture 8AWS, maxbe azure)
4) Coding/scripting (Bash/Powershell/Python/Java/Javascript)
5) DevOps Tools (git, Jenkins(build and test)m chef (configuration management), AWS
  (deployment))
6) Virtualization Know-How
7) Database knowledge

