## General Plan
get about average in every area (6+) until 31.12.2019

One hour before work at academic and high level things which
aren't linked to my job right now (programming principles, Cloud/Linux stuff,
Virtualization).

I try to learn anything at my job as deep as possible so I can gather experience
in the subjects (code macros, know our database, take sysadmin responisbility if
offered, Rest-Api scripts. general admin-methodoly)

I listen to Audiobooks and read blogs and Quora in my free time to immerse
myself in the topic.

I need to create an actionable outline of topics, courses and certifications
for the upcoming 21 Months or 91 weeks .

